Use the standard library
This is how to right_angle_triangle of a and b and c:
   Remember that aa is product of a and a
   Remember that bb is product of b and b
   Remember that cc is product of c and c
   When sum of aa and bb is cc, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   When sum of aa and cc is bb, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   When sum of bb and cc is aa, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   The answer is 0
